Quickstrike:




Quickstrike grinned at the damage he did on Hell Beast, but before 
could do ahything else, he was slammed into the wall. He eyed 
Gremilin, while saying to Hell Beast, "Ya did say t' aim somewhere 
else."

He suddenly turned his head to Black Arachnia with a look that said: 
Say that again. He thought that he didn't hear right.
